    {
      "role": "assistant",
      "content": "Subject: Notice of Disciplinary Action for Tardiness\n\nDear [Employee's Name],\n\nI hope this message finds you well. I am writing to address a matter of concern regarding your recent tardiness to work. Over the past two weeks, you have arrived approximately 15 minutes late on most days, which is a deviation from the expected punctuality outlined in your employment terms.\n\nAs a company, we understand that unforeseen circumstances can occasionally cause delays. However, consistent tardiness can disrupt the workflow and affect team dynamics. We value your contributions and would like to remind you that punctuality is a critical component of your role.\n\nWe kindly request that you adhere to the scheduled start times for your shifts moving forward. Failure to do so may result in further disciplinary action, as per the company's policies.\n\nThank you for your understanding and cooperation. We appreciate your attention to this matter and look forward to your timely arrivals in the future.\n\nBest regards,\n\n[Your Name]  \n[Your Position]  \n[Company Name]  \n[Contact Information]",
      "source": "target",
